name: INCallRecordResolutionResult
desc: A resolution result for the details of a call.

items.name: class func confirmationRequired(with: INCallRecord?) -> Self
items.desc: Creates a result that requires the user to confirm the value before proceeding.

items.name: class func disambiguation(with: [INCallRecord]) -> Self
items.desc: Creates a result that requires the user to select from an array of choices.

items.name: class func success(with: INCallRecord) -> Self
items.desc: Creates a result that contains the call record that matches the users request.
